information: prosol shapes innovative solutions for a wide range of nutritional products. since the beginning of its activity, in 1974, prosol has been governed by its core values: innovation and biotechnology research in each of its business area. prosol manufactures nutritional ingredients for infant formula, food and animal nutrition supplements, to improve immune response, performance and enhance food taste while respecting natural processes. thanks to its in-house developed technology, prosol production is totally sustainable, without the use of organic chemical solvents. prosol is one of the three major world producer of ribonucleic acid (rna) from yeast through organic solvents free process and one of the very few in europe. prosol projects, studies and develops the following concepts: - ribonucleic acids (rnas) and nucleotides for infant formula, dietary supplements, ffoods and animal nutrition. - the last year research resulted in three new brands targeted to contribute to critical breeding phases in different animal species: i-care, swinemod, petmod - petmod-artro, petmod-intestinal, petmod-leimun: a brand new line of pet complementary feeds based on nucleotides, specifically seized on specific nutritional needs - ribodiet: recent studies confirmed to be beneficial as support in the most common neurodegenerative diseases - active saccharomyces cerevisiae yeast additives for animal nutrition. prosol is iso9001, iso14001, gmp+, ifs, ohsas 18001 certified.

information: the entire mullerone project with the use of ozone is totally innovative because it proposes and realizes an extraction of slime in total well-being of the molluscs, obtaining a product of high chemical and organoleptic quality, far from that of burrs extracted with invasive and stressful stimulators (vinegar, salt ...) used until now. the percentages of mucopolysaccharides and proteins found in mullerone slime are very high and therefore of greater effectiveness in the anti-inflammatory, soothing, restructuring cells. the use of ozone allows an immediate sanitization of the extract through the elimination of most of the degenerative microorganisms and molds present on the body of the snail. the stimulating formula studied guarantees a physiological and non-invasive stress that does not affect the health of the animal in the production cycle the extracted slime has a very high shelf life and no longer undergoes fast degenerative processes. a very important fact: the snails used for extraction do not suffer biological damage or suffering. they can then be put back in the pens or be sold as soon as they get out of the machine. the evidence confirms that farmed molluscs, if well fed and validly irrigated in the pens, can be subjected to multiple extractions, without registering biological damage.
